## What Was Changed

### 1. CSS — Medical Spinner Component
**File:** [style.css](file:///c:/Users/Mayukh%20Jain/VS/NSOC/Medicsan_ai/static/css/style.css)

Added **~240 lines** of pure CSS animation for the spinner overlay:

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| **Pulse Ring** | Outer ring rotates with gradient colors, inner ring pulses with radial glow |
| **Medical Cross** | CSS-drawn cross icon at the center of the ring (gradient blue→purple) |
| **Heartbeat ECG Line** | Animated SVG path drawing a heartbeat waveform |
| **Shimmer Text** | "Analyzing..." label with gradient text + shimmer animation |
| **Sublabel** | Fading "Querying Groq AI..." contextual text |
| **Skeleton Bars** | 3 shimmer loading bars below the spinner |
| **Background Sweep** | Subtle gradient sweep across the overlay card |
| **Light Theme** | Full light theme support via `:root[data-theme="light"]` overrides |

The overlay uses `display: none` by default and `display: flex` when `.active` is added.

